 </a>
 <a href="/blog/screen-printing-vs-embroidery-construction/" class="group border border-hairline bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-gold-500">
 <h3 class="font-heading text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-tight text-charcoal group-hover:text-gold-600">Screen Print vs Embroidery</h3>
 <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-ash">Which decoration method holds up on outdoor crew gear.</p>
 </a>
 </div>
 </div>
 </section>

