 <section class="relative isolate overflow-hidden bg-navy-950">
 <img src="/images/generated/cta-bluehour.jpg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 h-full w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
 <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-navy-950/80"></div>
 <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-24 text-center sm:px-6 sm:py-28 lg:px-8">
 <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-extrabold uppercase leading-[0.95] tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">Outfit your crew for <span class="text-gold-400">the desert, not the catalog.</span></h2>
 <p class="mx-auto mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy-200">Send your logo. Stocked tees and long-sleeves on hand.</p>
